nodes.title: 0-1 IMAGE Prompt
widgets_values:
A modern office building, featuring a ground floor and three upper levels and consists of two façades. The left facade includes vertical green-tinted glass columns between textured beige sandstone walls with a rough and natural finish.

Left Façade:

(The left facade has two polished, green marble cladding located in the horizontal borders of the left facade, both are protruded from the left facade, one strip is above the ground floor in the left facade and one strip is at the roofline of the left facade, catching direct sunlight with subtle reflections. Avoid green marble cladding on all areas except the far-left and far-right edges of the left façade; exclude green marble from central sections, right façade, roof, and ground floor; no green marble on window frames or middle columns; prevent green marble from appearing on unintended surfaces.:1.5)

Vertical rhythmic divisions with tall green glass sections framed in beige sandstone.

Smooth, high-quality stone—not blocky or irregular.

The glass reflects the blue sky and surrounding structures.

Right Façade:

Aluminum-framed windows with dark green-tinted glazing.

Beige stucco wall texture, smoothly finished and slightly warm-toned.

Scene:

Two luxury silver Porsche cars passing on a smooth asphalt street with curbs.

A lush green tree on the right side of the image.

People walking near the building, slightly motion-blurred.

Captured from a low-angle perspective.

Bright, sunny day with a clear blue sky, soft white clouds, and lens flare.

Sun positioned high (approx. 80° altitude), casting crisp shadows and enhancing the building’s form.

Atmosphere:

Emphasis on contemporary elegance and traditional materials blended in a clean, professional architectural visualization.
